### Create a Product (Admin / Needs Bearer Token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Budget Smartphone",
  "price": 9999,
  "discountPrice": 8999,
  "category": "Electronics",
  "stock": 50,
  "description": "A very affordable high performance smartphone.",
  "variants": [
    { "color": "Black", "stock": 25 },
    { "color": "Blue", "stock": 25 }
  ]
}

### Get all Products (with Pagination & Filters)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?keyword=Smart&category=Electronics&maxPrice=10000

### Get Single Product
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products/<PRODUCT_ID>

### Soft Delete Product
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/<PRODUCT_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <YOUR_TOKEN_HERE>
